      "id": 733638,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "The report identifies an issue in the biography field on addons.allizom.org where the application's restriction on using links can be bypassed using protocol-relative URLs. Despite the explicit policy against links, users can embed functional hyperlinks using the syntax <a href=\"//evil.com\">click</a>, which successfully creates clickable links that redirect to external websites.\n\nThe restriction on using links is mainly to avoid spam and not necessarily a security control, therefore, the severity of bypassing the restriction is low.",
